props.name: LEGGACY: Teslegg Model F
props.description: (2019) After a long wait Teslegg has released their mass market fusion powered car! Fusion eggs are in high demand.

props.name: Your First Contract
props.description: We heard you are open to contract work! Help fill this order from the local pharmacy!

props.name: LEGGACY: A Clever Solution
props.description: As drought wreaks havoc on agriculture, farmers are looking for water in unusual places... (2018)

props.name: Orbital Fueling
props.description: A new orbital fueling rig has begun operation, it needs copious amounts of Quantum Eggs!

props.name: Space Food
props.description: A biomedical firm is developing food for space travelers based heavily on superfood eggs.

props.name: LEGGACY: Mother's Day Brunch
props.description: Mothers all over the galaxy are requesting omelettes and french toast for breakfast! (2018)

props.name: LEGGACY: Complex Costumes
props.description: Halloween (2018) costume manufacturing has started. These are sophisticated scary costumes that need some high tech components.

props.name: Cool Off
props.description: As heat waves take over the country, waterballoons are in short supply!

props.name: LEGGACY: Chocolate!
props.description: Didn't take scientists long to figure out the smart thing to do was to just make chickens lay chocolate eggs. (2018)

props.name: Made In Space
props.description: A space exploration firm is building a spaceship factory.. in space!

props.name: Bluetooth Pigs
props.description: Bluetooth enabled pigs are the new hot pet! Neuro-implant makers need more materials!

props.name: Color Change
props.description: As the leaves change color so do the eggs. Help meet seasonal demand!

props.name: LEGGACY: Fall Festival Competition
props.description: The (2018) Fall Festival egg laying competition is here!

props.name: LEGGACY: Super Food Drive
props.description: (2018) Egg Farmers have flocked to high value eggs leaving people hungry! We need some Superfood eggs stat!

props.name: Fall Flu
props.description: Flu season is getting started, and folks are stocking up preventative medications!

props.name: LEGGACY: Pumpkin Crunch
props.description: (2018) Pumpkins are in super high demand... leave it to the chickens to deliver the goods!

props.name: Hydrogen Dreams
props.description: After a hydrogen fuel cell car company was revealed to be a fraud, Teslegg Fusion car sales are surging!

props.name: LEGGACY: A New Sun
props.description: (2018) A new solar system has been found with multiple habitable planets in need of terraforming!

props.name: Quantum Ballot Box
props.description: The new Quantum Ballot boxes can securely store millions of ballots. Make sure you (or your parents) are planning to vote!

props.name: LEGGACY: Moon Food
props.description: (2019) Moon colony food stores were tainted without government food inspectors to check for contaminants. Help send some food!

props.name: Last Minute Decoration
props.description: Family meetings were called, one common conclusion: We need more pumpkins!

props.name: Tricker Treats
props.description: Time to help make everyone's favorite Halloween treat!

props.name: LEGGACY: Halloween Blitz
props.description: (2018) Pumpkin demand is overwhelming! A quick contract for big money!

props.name: Prototypes
props.description: SpaceEggs is prototyping giant rockets at an incredible pace. Supplies are needed!

props.name: Tachyon Deflector
props.description: Researchers are developing a device to prevent the adverse effects of deep space travel on the human body.

props.name: LEGGACY: Moon Rockets
props.description: Moon colony food stores were tainted. The food is ready on earth, just need more fuel! (2019)

props.name: More Pie
props.description: Even with holiday travel at all time lows, the demand for pumpkin pie has never been higher!

props.name: Small Reactors
props.description: The popularity of new compact dilithium reactors are spiking demand for the fuel!

props.name: Leftovers
props.description: (2018) Thanksgiving has left the world with too many leftovers, quantum Tupperware is sold out everywhere, and more raw materials are needed.

props.name: LEGGACY: Wildfires
props.description: (2018) Climate change is wreaking havoc on dryer climates. Wildfires are rampant but now there is a way egg farmers can help! (Egg, Inc. has donated $500 to the American Red Cross)

props.name: LEGGACY: Fusion Tankers
props.description: The world's largest ocean shipping company is putting ultra compact fusion reactors in all their tankers. Long term work available.(2018)

props.name: Quantum Monday
props.description: With nearly all Holiday shopping happening online, Quantum storage solutions are in high demand!

props.name: Toy Builders
props.description: Toy sales are off the charts this year with manufacturers scrambling to buy raw materials!

props.name: LEGGACY: World Record Egg
props.description: (2019) With a simple picture of an Egg becoming the most liked social media post, demand for the classic is booming!

props.name: Winter Break
props.description: (2018) It's Winter Break! And since break homework was deemed cruel and unusual punishment, Prodigy Eggs are all the rage!

props.name: Holidegg
props.description: Tasty holiday food and drink such as Egg Nog and Noodle Kugel are spiking demand for regular eggs!

props.name: Space Food 2.0
props.description: Engineered foods based on Superfood eggs are in mass production for deep space travel. Ingredients needed!

props.name: Space Bots
props.description: New tiny space robots have been developed to explore space, small enough to be launched with traditional fuels!

props.name: LEGGACY: The Thaw
props.description: (2019) Half the USA is frozen over from an Arctic Blast! Fusion egg reserves are depleted for home heaters and de-icers.

props.name: LEGGACY: Resolutions
props.description: It's that time of year, everyone is headed to the gym and getting on a strict diet of Superfood Eggs!

props.name: 2020 Hangover
props.description: Is it possible to have a hangover from a year? Doctors are prescribing medical eggs to patients with mysterious headaches and nausea.

props.name: LEGGACY: Quantum Trash Bags
props.description: (2018) With all the wrapping paper and boxes to throw out, Quantum Trash bags are flying off the shelves!

props.name: Ion Drive II
props.description: The once experimental high thrust ion drive is now ready for test flights. Fusion eggs needed!

props.name: LEGGACY: History Lesson
props.description: (2019) In appreciation of Martin Luther King day people around the world take a trip back to witness first hand key moments in world history!

props.name: Lost Civilizations
props.description: The boom in deeps space travel has led to the discovery of strange items. Scientists need materials to prototype containers to harness their unusual energy signature.

props.name: Quantum Payload
props.description: With the recent boom in Artifacts exploration, quantum crates are in mass production!

props.name: Tachyon Tube
props.description: Heralded as 'Time Tourism for the masses', the new Tachyon Tube allows viewing of historical events from the comfort of your living room.

props.name: LEGGACY: Galactic Outreach
props.description: (2019) An emerging civilization needs to fight a health epidemic but is not ready for more advanced eggs. We need your help!

props.name: LEGGACY: Laurel vs Yanny
props.description: (2018) A Quantum rift is causing people to hear different words in a viral video. Scientists have a fix but they need your help.

props.name: LEGGACY: Space Vacation
props.description: (2019) Space Tourism is way up this year and there are rocket fuel shortages everywhere!

props.name: Clean Crypto
props.description: Crypto currency mining energy use is out of control! Good thing we have a virtually unlimited source of clean energy now.

props.name: LEGGACY: Love is in the Air
props.description: (2019) Valentine's day is here and boxes of chocolates are flying of the shelf!

props.name: Coco Cleanse
props.description: After an indulgent holiday, folks are looking to make up for it. Supplies are needed!

props.name: The Thaw
props.description: After a winter storm wreaked havoc on parts of the country, materials are needed to repair and rebuild.
